overview: TransSensual is pleased to present the second volume of the popular naughty nurses series. Sexy nurse Korra Del Rio has her hands full with handsome patient Lance Hart. She does her best to reassure him that everything will be just fine. In homage to Kill Bill, gorgeous assassin Natassia Dreams, disguised as a nurse, arrives to finish off another assassin played by D. Arclyte. Things don't go quite as planned, but the outcome will surely be pleasurable. Gabriel Delassandro is recuperating when his home nurse, Domino Presley, arrives ready to help ease his aches. Finally, emo cutie Ruckus is at home studying when he gets a surprise visit by Natalie Mars, who is a strip-a-gram nurse. Natalie is embarrassed to discover she is at the wrong house, and Ruckus does his best to make her feel better.
title: TS Nurses 2
